---------------------------------------------
ABOUT THE TOOLKIT:
---------------------------------------------
- Operating System Agnostic! 
  > Windows
  > Mac OS X
  > Other Unix flavours

- Requriements
  > Apache or similar web server
  > Toolkit Folders
  > Nothing to install. Just copy the folders and you are good to go

- Application templates available
  > Download a Git demo folder
  > make it yours

- Site creation is made easy
  > make.site <your site name> is all it takes

- Batteries are included
  > Twitter Bootstrap
  > others

